c: 33
v: 49
t: "Aey logon jo iman laye ho, jab tum momin auraton se nikah karo aur phir unhein haath lagane se pehle talaq de do to tumhari taraf se unpar koi iddat (waiting period) lazim nahin hai jiske pooray honay ka tum mutalba kar sako. Lihaza unhein kuch maal do aur bhale tareeqe se rukhsat kardo"